      <title>Scope 称极右翼可能因 5000 亿欧元投资计划而激怒欧盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/far-right-may-irk-eu-in-500-billion-investment-push-scope-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Scope Ratings 表示，极右翼政党可能阻碍欧盟填补每年 5000 亿欧元（5380 亿美元）的投资缺口，这使得资本市场的汇集变得更加迫切。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/far-right-may-irk-eu-in-500-billion-investment-push-scope-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 11:07:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
